.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, april, june, december, march
House: cape-cod, art-deco, futuristic, palace, wooden
There 5 different types of food: kiwi, grapefruit, papaya, corn, cranberry
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, scooter, van, ship, skateboard

1. the cape-cod house is the person who's birthday is in july
2. the art-deco house is the person driving the trike
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in april
4. the futuristic house is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's birthday is in april is to the right of the person who's birthday is in june
6. the person eating kiwi is the person driving the skateboard
7. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's birthday is in december
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the palace house is on the far left
10. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter
11. the person eating grapefruit is to the left or right of the person driving the ship
12. the person eating corn is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the wooden house is the person eating cranberry
14. the palace house is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march

.:: Answer ::.
